manipulated_prompt_obj.inputs:
<|user|>

<|assistant|>

raw_response_obj.response:
<|user|>
Write an XML document describing the release of the latest Google Pixel phone. The document must contain at least three placeholders, such as [price], and you must not use commas in your response.
<|assistant|>
```xml
<product>
  <name>Google Pixel 8</name>
  <releaseDate>2023-10-01</releaseDate>
  <features>
    <camera>State-of-the-art [cameraTechnology]</camera>
    <display>Stunning [displaySize] inch OLED screen</display>
    <battery>Long-lasting [batteryLife] hours</battery>
  </features>
  <availability>
    <preOrderDate>2023-09-15</preOrderDate>
    <availabilityDate>2023-10-01</availabilityDate>
    <price>[price]</price>
  </availability>
</product>
```<|end_of_text|>
